textMap.PRIMARY: Joel de la Fuente: Joel de la Fuente was raised in Evanston, Illinois, and graduated from the North Shore Country Day School in Winnetka, Illinois, in 1987.

DJ Qualls: Booked his first lead, Kyle, in Road Trip (2000), after auditioning for a one line part at an Atlanta casting office. The director invited him to meet Ivan Reitman in his Beverly Hills office, where he was cast.
Stephen Root: Donated $100,000 to the University of Florida in 2003 to fund an acting studio, which is now called the Stephen Root Acting Studio.
